            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-f09fcd twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-6b4cd0\"><p>第十回     莫坡寺瘸師入佛肚　任吳張夢授永兒法</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/5bcf7de9f61cc8f5/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
