            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5bcf7de9f61cc8f5/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-f09fcd twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
