            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5bcf7de9f61cc8f5/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-f09fcd twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-6b4cd0\"><p>International donations are gratefully accepted, but we cannot make\nany statements concerning tax treatment of donations received from\noutside the United States.  U.S. laws alone swamp our small staff.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/5bcf7de9f61cc8f5/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5bcf7de9f61cc8f5/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-f09fcd twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-6b4cd0\"><p>Please check the Project Gutenberg Web pages for current donation\nmethods and addresses.  Donations are accepted in a number of other\nways including checks, online payments and credit card donations.\nTo donate, please visit: http://pglaf.org/donate</p></div>"
