            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/5bcf7de9f61cc8f5/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-f09fcd twpub-5bcf7de9f61cc8f5-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Project Gutenberg-tm eBooks are often created from several printed\neditions, all of which are confirmed as Public Domain in the U.S.\nunless a copyright notice is included.  Thus, we do not necessarily\nkeep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</p></div>"
